02:47.703 --> 02:49.671
Sorry for the wait, Nurse Nevin.

02:49.705 --> 02:51.607
Ms. Thorpe can see you now.

02:55.110 --> 02:56.912
Please, come in.

02:56.945 --> 02:59.848
- This is Joshua Williams,
head of risk management. -Hi.

03:01.216 --> 03:03.552
Um, what is this about?

03:03.585 --> 03:06.187
Unfortunately,
we have some bad news. Please.

03:10.926 --> 03:14.496
Lily's family is suing
the hospital for wrongful death.

03:14.530 --> 03:15.897
And you're named in the suit.

03:17.365 --> 03:19.401
Uh, I don't understand.

03:19.435 --> 03:21.202
- Just me?
- No.

03:21.236 --> 03:23.672
However, risk management
has to do their investigation,

03:23.705 --> 03:26.875
and until its over, we have to
ask you to stop seeing patients.

03:28.309 --> 03:30.278
Has Lily's autopsy come back?

03:30.311 --> 03:33.014
We'll go over all the details
during the investigation.

03:33.048 --> 03:35.451
Ms. Thorpe.

03:35.484 --> 03:36.752
There's been an emergency
in the OR.

03:36.785 --> 03:39.421
A patient caught fire.

03:41.089 --> 03:43.459
You've done enough damage,
I've got it from here.

03:43.492 --> 03:45.427
I'm his surgeon, you're an
internist. What are you even

03:45.461 --> 03:46.928
- doing on the OR floor?
- He had a latex allergy.

03:46.962 --> 03:48.363
I was double-checking nothing
was missed.

03:48.396 --> 03:50.899
- The proper precautions were taken.
- What happened?

03:50.932 --> 03:52.968
Your chief of surgery
just set a patient on fire.

03:53.001 --> 03:54.536
Look, I've just had it.
I've had it with you!

03:54.570 --> 03:56.204
- Challenging me at every corner.
- Not now. Dr. Hawkins,

03:56.237 --> 03:58.106
go to the ICU;
Dr. Bell, a word.

03:59.741 --> 04:01.710
What the hell happened in there?

04:01.743 --> 04:03.879
Well, it's unclear,
but it wasn't my fault.

04:03.912 --> 04:07.616
Oh, just like Mr. Zhou's post-op
bleeding wasn't your fault?

04:07.649 --> 04:09.785
I don't know
what you think you know.

04:09.818 --> 04:11.820
You know what I know?
Is that I have recording devices

04:11.853 --> 04:13.722
in every OR,
so I'm gonna find out exactly

04:13.755 --> 04:14.856
what caused that fire.

